{
  "stem": "13382.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what they did, anything which was their food, they [? all ?] [? sort of ?] collected and put it in that-- in their-- sort of their wagons which they brought.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meantime, some of-- a lot of the boys had a chance to get to the telephone and phoned the American military police.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So while this was going on, the American military police came and surrounded the-- the Austrian police.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the whole thing was straightened out, that this is no drugs, nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we are not involved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are sort of Zionists.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we're going to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we're not sort of dealing in anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they commanded the Austrian police, they have to put back everything to the place where it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day, we got a message that we should-- better leave Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they will get us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because Vienna was the first point of arrival.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From there on, all the distribution went everywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that was the place--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they still tried to look or organize some further passage for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This-- that was an illegal movement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to fool the British.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over land.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we went-- we had to-- we moved from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because coming to-- you see, we had to-- I mean, the Bricha was working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we had-- against the Russian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Russian didn't want to-- the-- the-- the English was very much against it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Americans supported us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, you know, there was sort of a confusion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it has to be planned in a very sort of a proper way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was not quite pre-arranged, but there was some chance that they could accommodate us in Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
